data.description:
Beautiful house on a nice cul-de-sac lot! This home features huge valuted ceilings in the living and dining rooms. The master bedroom is downstairs, master bathroom offers a walk in shower. Upstairs offers 2 bedrooms with a full bathroom. 

The kitchen has tons of storage space and an upgraded oven which also works as an air fryer and the built in microwave is also a convection oven. 

There are no homes behind the house. There is a huge grass field and park that can be accessed through a access path one house away.
